resources.description: Pure water is a kind of water that removes harmful matter as well as mineral substance and trace elements, but pure water is harmful to one’s health if drinking for a long period. We improve the way to produce healthy natural water by substituting reverse osmosis for super filtering technique.
resources.name: Produce Natural Drinking Water By Super Filter Technique
